data.title: Eugenio Maria De Hostos Microsociety School - Jobs
data.meta_description: Eugenio Maria De Hostos Microsociety School is a regular public magnet school. It is one of 40 schools in Yonkers City School District. Eugenio Maria De Hostos Microsociety School has an enrollment of 592 students in grades PK-08. Enrollment has decreased -1% to -5% over the last year.
